snippet.textDisplay: I love this song, it is filled with all the good things , makes you smile and dance and Faris's contribution to the feel of the song is amazing..he is a star ..the ladies were so cute, I loved their singing, I am blown away by the little one also , what swag, and talent , Umair is legit punjabi singer , I am not that into punjabi songs but I am loving this one ..I can watch the video everyday without getting bored..again, coke studio is an audio visual experience and the team never ceases to amaze, entertain, revive, celebrate our pakistani culture , show how open and easy it can be blended with the world without trying hard , how it is so relatable and universal as well as authentic...so much love for Zulfi...he deserves pride of performance award for what he has brought to the world through coke studio.❤
